custom_item_2.solution:
Use this command to configure Network Time Protocol (NTP) servers.
config system ntp
 set ntpsync {enable | disable}
 set source-ipset syncintervalset type {fortiguard | custom}
 set server-mode {enable | disable}
 set interfaceconfig ntpserver
   editset authentication {enable | disable}
    set keyset key-idset ntpv3 {enable | disable}
    set server[/]
   end
end

