custom_item_5.solution:
Use this command to configure higher security requirements for administrator passwords and
IPsec VPN pre-shared keys.

config system password-policy
 set status {enable | disable}
 set apply-to [admin-password ipsec-preshared-key]
 set change-4-characters {enable | disable}
 set expireset minimum-lengthset min-lower-case-letterset min-upper-case-letterset min-non-alphanumericset min-numberset expire-status {enable | disable}
 set expire-dayend

